data.description: Charming and cozy, this adorable one-and-a-half-story 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled in Vesili, a quaint small town, within the sought-after New Prague School District. Situated conveniently across the street from a picturesque pond, a serene church, and baseball fields, it offers a sense of community and leisure. This solidly built home features the primary bedroom on the main level, complete with a full bathroom. Bathed in natural sunlight, it exudes warmth and comfort, creating a welcoming atmosphere. With its delightful charm and fantastic location, this home is perfect for those seeking a tranquil and sunny retreat.
